              <h4> Ordering Fractions on a Number Line (Slides 6- 7) 25 minutes</h4> 
              <p>Pairs will engage in placing given fractions on a number line
                  and participate in a discussion about strategies used and
                  fraction concepts that are needed to successfully complete
                  this task</p> <br> 
              <h4>Connecting the Number line to Probability (Slides 8 - 12) 10 minutes</h4> 
              <p>Participants place events on a (0 to 1) number line based on
                  the likelihood that the event will occur. They will discuss
                  connections of probability concepts to fractions thinking.
                  Connections to curriculum for Grades 4 to 6 will also be
                  made.</p>
            </td>
