                <li> What is the challenge of this task if you choose to use common denominators to complete this task? </li>
                <li> How does changing the fractions to decimals support student understanding of fractions?</li>
              </ul>
            </td>
            <td>
              <ul>
                <li> I didn’t realize that there were so many different strategies that I could use to graph these fractions</li>
                <li> This is a good activity for students to learn that a fraction is a number</li>
